	<section class="article-content clearfix" itemprop="articleBody">
		<p>Chronic disease accounts for the bulk of all health care costs in the US. <a href="http://www.nationalhealthcouncil.org/NHC_Files/Pdf_Files/AboutChronicDisease.pdf" target="_blank">Seven out of every 10 Americans who die each year </a>(more than 1.7 million people) die of a chronic disease and 80% of chronic diseases are preventable.</p>
<p>Persivia’s Population Health and Risk Management Solution introduces new capabilities to the population health management marketplace. Our solution combines claims-based risk stratification with clinically-rich care gap analyses. This allows us to not only identify high-risk patients, but also uncover those patients within the high strata that have the most actionable clinical opportunities for improvement. The solution allows users to focus limited resources on the areas that are positioned for the most improvement.</p>	</section>
	
